OL,3,CAnger as 'no progress is made' to help
OL,4,Cflood-hit businesses
OL,6,FBusiness owners in Clevedon say they
OL,7,Fare losing money because the local
OL,8,Fauthority is failing to clear flood
OL,9,Fwater fast enough.
OL,11,FSeveral businesses in The Triangle say
OL,12,Fthey have repeatedly had to close and
OL,13,Fturn customers away due to flooding
OL,14,Fcaused by poor drainage.
OL,16,FAfter recent heavy rain, several shops
OL,17,Fhad to temporarily shut their doors.
