OL,3,CAnger as 'no progress is made' to help
OL,4,Cflood-hit businesses
OL,6,FA North Somerset Council spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're aware of localised
OL,8,Fflooding at the Triangle in Clevedon,
OL,9,Fand we understand the impact this is
OL,10,Fhaving on the local community.
OL,12,F"We've designed drainage improvement
OL,13,Fworks to help resolve this issue.
OL,14,FWe're working closely with Wessex
OL,15,FWater to progress this, as they
OL,16,Fmaintain the sewers in North Somerset.
OL,17,FWe're meeting with them again this
OL,18,Fweek, and we hope to have positive
OL,19,Fupdates to share soon.
