OL,3,CAnger as 'no progress is made' to help
OL,4,Cflood-hit businesses
OL,6,F"As a council, we're responsible for
OL,7,Fmaintaining all the gullies and drains
OL,8,Fon public land in North Somerset. We
OL,9,Flook after around 44,000 gullies on
OL,10,Fthe public highway, as well as their
OL,11,Fconnections to the drainage system
OL,12,Falong roads. Please report any road
OL,13,Fdrainage problems to us online at
OL,14,Fwww.n-somerset.gov.uk/drainage."
