OL,6,FA Wessex Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Drainage systems carrying floodwater
OL,8,Fare often interconnected so we're
OL,9,Fworking closely with North Somerset
OL,10,FCouncil, who are responsible for
OL,11,Fhighway drains, to help resolve the
OL,12,Fdistressing issues for businesses at
OL,13,FThe Triangle and advise on how future
OL,14,Fflood risk can be managed.
